---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="Cappuccino.io affiliate disclosure — how we earn money, what it means for our recommendations, and your rights as a reader."
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-22 pb-28">

    <header class="mb-16">
      <p class="small-caps font-body text-caption text-espresso/45 tracking-widest mb-6">
        Legal
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink max-w-[18ch]">
        Affiliate Disclosure
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-small text-espresso/50 mt-4">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="max-w-[65ch] space-y-8">

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h4 text-ink mb-4">What this disclosure covers</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
          Cappuccino.io participates in affiliate marketing programmes. This means
          that some links on this site — to products on Amazon, retailers, or brand
          websites — are affiliate links. If you click one of these links and make a
          purchase, we may receive a commission. The commission comes from the
          retailer, not from you. You pay the same price whether or not you use our
          link.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h4 text-ink mb-4">FTC compliance</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
          The United States Federal Trade Commission (FTC) requires websites to
          clearly disclose material connections between the site and the products or
          services it promotes. This page, and the disclosure notice on every
          article that contains affiliate links, satisfies this requirement.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75] mt-4">
          We include an affiliate disclosure banner at the top of every article
          that contains affiliate links. We do not bury disclosures in footers or
          use language that obscures the nature of the relationship.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h4 text-ink mb-4">How this affects our recommendations</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
          Our editorial recommendations are based on testing, research, and
          our specific evaluation criteria for cappuccino-making. We do not
          recommend products we haven't evaluated, do not write positive reviews
          in exchange for payment, and do not rank products based on commission
          rate.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75] mt-4">
          In some cases we may recommend a product that does not have an
          affiliate programme. We will link to it regardless. Conversely, we
          decline to recommend products that we cannot stand behind, regardless
          of affiliate availability.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h4 text-ink mb-4">The Brands directory</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
          The{' '}
          <a
            href="/brands"
            class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-espresso/30 hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150"
          >
            Brands page
          </a>{' '}
          is a paid directory. Brands listed there have paid for a placement
          listing. This is disclosed on that page. The editorial content of this
          site — reviews, guides, technique articles — is produced independently
          and is not influenced by paid directory relationships.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h4 text-ink mb-4">Programmes we participate in</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
          We currently participate in the Amazon Associates programme, among others.
          Amazon Associates is an affiliate advertising programme designed to provide
          a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to
          Amazon.com.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-h4 text-ink mb-4">Questions</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
          If you have questions about this disclosure or our editorial practices,
          write to{' '}
          <a
            href="mailto:contact@cappuccino.io"
            class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-espresso/30 hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150"
          >
            contact@cappuccino.io
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
